NEVER BEEN INFLATED!

04:47.354 --> 04:52.624
[screams and then laughter]

04:52.626 --> 04:57.062
Did I ever tell you about the
night the mannequin came to life

04:57.064 --> 04:59.498
and haunted all the costumes?

04:59.500 --> 05:00.999
What happened?

05:01.001 --> 05:02.567
I just told you, darling.

05:02.569 --> 05:04.503
A mannequin came to life and
haunted all the costumes.

05:04.505 --> 05:05.537
