doing here? Is everything OK?

05:11.412 --> 05:15.380
Everything is fine. In
fact, it's more than fine.

05:15.382 --> 05:18.717
I've decided to join you in your
Nightmare Night festivities.

05:20.620 --> 05:23.555
Seriously? You?
Out? Tonight?

05:25.525 --> 05:27.726
Every Nightmare Night I
shut myself in my cottage

05:27.728 --> 05:29.494
and refuse to come
out until morning.

05:29.496 --> 05:31.563
But it's just like when
I was afraid to sing

05:31.565 --> 05:32.998
in front of anypony.

05:33.000 --> 05:34.800
If I hadn't given it a try,

05:34.802 --> 05:37.669
I never would've found
out how much I enjoy it.

05:37.671 --> 05:40.672
And we'd have missed out
on how great you sound.

05:40.674 --> 05:43.041
Fluttershy with us
on Nightmare Night?

05:43.043 --> 05:44.976
Why that's positively
the most wonderful news

05:44.978 --> 05:47.346
I've heard in ages!

05:47.348 --> 05:49.514
You can get dressed up
in a costume with us

05:49.516 --> 05:50.882
and play Nightmare
Night games with us

05:50.884 --> 05:52.517
and eat candy apples with us!

05:52.519 --> 05:54.586
Don't forget the best part.

05:54.588 --> 05:57.089
Goin' through my
family's corn maze.

05:57.091 --> 05:59.758
Oh, right. The maze.

05:59.760 --> 06:02.994
Only if you're up for it.

06:02.996 --> 06:06.698
I am! I am ready to
take on Nightmare Night!

06:06.700 --> 06:08.767
AAAHHH!

06:08.769 --> 06:14.439
[nervous laughter]
Just practicing.

06:20.046 --> 06:22.948
