08:06.118 --> 08:09.187
I get it! You're a robber
escaping into the night!

08:09.189 --> 08:11.923
You're a NINJA escaping
into the night!

08:11.925 --> 08:14.726
YOU'RE BLACK LICORICE
escaping into the night!

08:14.728 --> 08:18.663
Close. I'm going to a masquerade
ball. Without the mask.

08:20.700 --> 08:24.236
Oh, that's great!
Isn't it great?

08:24.238 --> 08:25.704
Oh, yeah.

08:25.706 --> 08:26.571
