know I was under attack?

09:33.039 --> 09:35.040
Time for candy!

09:35.042 --> 09:36.074
It is?

09:36.076 --> 09:37.342
I made candy bags!

09:37.344 --> 09:39.911
Each bag has been made
with each of YOU in mind,

09:39.913 --> 09:42.213
complete with each of
your favorite candies!

09:43.783 --> 09:44.849
Awesome!

09:47.153 --> 09:50.822
Here. Take it. Take it!
What are you waiting for?

09:50.824 --> 09:52.624
Well, it's just...

09:52.626 --> 09:55.026
