the fun out of it, aren't I?

10:12.913 --> 10:15.614
You're not taking
out ALL the fun.

10:15.616 --> 10:16.915
Just like, 90 per--

10:16.917 --> 10:18.249
[clang]

10:18.251 --> 10:19.618
--some of it.

10:19.620 --> 10:21.686
I really want to do this.

10:21.688 --> 10:25.390
But there's just so many things
that terrify me about tonight,

10:25.392 --> 10:27.959
I couldn't possibly predict
what might upset me.

10:31.397 --> 10:35.233
Unless... YOU were the
one doing the scaring!

10:35.235 --> 10:42.173
HER scaring US?
[hooting laughter]

10:42.175 --> 10:44.743
Oh, you're being serious.

10:44.745 --> 10:46.811
The thing you hate
is being scared,

10:46.813 --> 10:51.983
but if YOU'RE the one
doing the scaring then...

10:51.985 --> 10:54.185
....then I can help
you all have fun,

10:54.187 --> 10:57.022
and I can still be a
part of Nightmare Night!

10:57.024 --> 10:59.024
So you like that idea?

10:59.026 --> 11:00.692
I think I do!

11:00.694 --> 11:02.761
