There's nopony there!

12:24.478 --> 12:29.147
<i>That's right. Because she</i>
<i>didn't care to show up!</i>

12:29.149 --> 12:30.782
What?

12:30.784 --> 12:32.317
<i>A friend who didn't</i>
<i>come through!</i>

12:32.319 --> 12:35.420
That must scare you to the core!

12:35.422 --> 12:37.989
<i>Quick, everypony,</i>
<i>look behind you!</i>

12:37.991 --> 12:40.859
Uh, what are those?

12:40.861 --> 12:45.296
<i>They're unplanned guests!</i>
<i>Your worst nightmare!</i>

12:45.298 --> 12:47.265
<i>You don't have</i>
<i>enough food for them!</i>

12:49.068 --> 12:53.138
<i>Oh, no! There's a tiny</i>
<i>kitten that needs a home!</i>

12:53.140 --> 12:55.540
<i>But you are</i>
<i>over-scheduled right now.</i>

12:55.542 --> 12:58.810
<i>You don't have time to help!</i>

12:58.812 --> 13:02.280
<i>I said, you don't</i>
<i>have time to help!</i>

13:04.917 --> 13:07.418
This should appear to scare you!

13:11.190 --> 13:14.125
Why don't you look terrified?
You showed up to a party

13:14.127 --> 13:16.494
and everypony was extremely
disappointed in you.

13:16.496 --> 13:19.464
Can you imagine
anything more upsetting?

13:19.466 --> 13:21.833
Rarity: It was a really
good try, darling

13:21.835 --> 13:23.201
but the scares at
Nightmare Night

13:23.203 --> 13:25.503
are of an entirely
different nature.

13:25.505 --> 13:28.106
It was really
creative, though.

13:28.108 --> 13:31.309
I never would have
thought of... all this.

13:32.878 --> 13:37.916
Oh, I'm just not cut out for
this. Just go on without me.

13:37.918 --> 13:40.318
Oh, no, we
couldn't possibly.

13:40.320 --> 13:44.322
You have to. This is the night
you look forward to all year.

13:44.324 --> 13:47.358
We could...stay here?

13:47.360 --> 13:50.829
It's OK. I really want
you all to have fun.

13:50.831 --> 13:53.064
This is how I spend
every Nightmare Night!

13:53.066 --> 13:57.402
Please go, I'll be fine.

13:57.404 --> 13:59.571
It's funny; I actually
thought she had an idea

13:59.573 --> 14:02.240
for something really
scary for a second there!

14:02.242 --> 14:04.075
She definitely
tried her hardest!

14:06.512 --> 14:09.113
I did try my hardest.

14:09.115 --> 14:12.917
[banging]

14:12.919 --> 14:15.186
Or maybe not.

14:15.188 --> 14:18.556
I suppose I could have gone
with something a bit scarier.

14:18.558 --> 14:22.327
You're right. I've
been taking baby steps.

14:22.329 --> 14:26.064
I think it's time
for grown up ones.

14:26.066 --> 14:28.967
I don't suppose you have any
ideas how I could do that?

14:28.969 --> 14:31.102
[growl]

14:33.607 --> 14:37.909
Everypony's lining up for the
corn maze, y'all. Let's go!

14:39.378 --> 14:41.913
Oh, yeah! I can't believe
we're finally doing this!

14:43.048 --> 14:44.115
[whinny]

14:44.117 --> 14:46.317
[screams]

14:46.319 --> 14:48.353
[laughter]

14:50.456 --> 14:52.957
It's a good thing
Fluttershy isn't here

14:52.959 --> 14:56.060
because she would NEVER
be able to handle this!

14:56.062 --> 14:58.529
