14:58.531 --> 15:03.234
[distant screams]

15:03.236 --> 15:09.073
<i>â™ª [tense music] </i>

15:09.075 --> 15:10.074
AGH!

15:10.076 --> 15:12.944
Boo...yup.

15:12.946 --> 15:15.246
[laughter]

15:17.116 --> 15:19.417
[crackling]

15:19.419 --> 15:25.390
What. Is. That. Sound?

15:25.392 --> 15:27.625
It looks like...bones!

15:27.627 --> 15:30.395
[screams]

15:30.397 --> 15:33.665
Looks like a bunch of dried
sticks painted white to me.

15:33.667 --> 15:37.368
Hey, TRY to keep up the
illusion, would ya?

15:37.370 --> 15:45.944
â™ª [eerie]

15:45.946 --> 15:48.146
[screams]

